      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add your <strong>arborio rice</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and your <strong>ground turmeric</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min</p><p>Add your <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong> and your <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong>, then cook for a further 1 min</p>",
